    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在漫画原作「游☆戏☆王」中活跃的角色将重聚在此「游戏王」经典数码游戏合辑中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包括众多首次在日本以外的海外地区发售的「游☆戏☆王」游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013550/extras/427bc6b3644c40e6ca828a8b24f68a4c.poster.avif?t=1740682738\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013550/extras/427bc6b3644c40e6ca828a8b24f68a4c.webm?t=1740682738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013550/extras/427bc6b3644c40e6ca828a8b24f68a4c.mp4?t=1740682738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>♦线上对战</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Monsters 4: Battle of Great Duelists!」可以进行线上对战,！部分游戏将在推出后更新以支持在线对战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>♦自定义游戏</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支援解锁隐藏角色和卡牌，从禁止和限制列表中移除卡组容量、决斗者等级和卡牌，自定义按键配置及其他选项。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>♦回放／快转</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用「回放」功能让时间倒转，或者「快转」功能观看您的策略展开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013550/extras/5f7d25f92dacef12c641f010bcfcfaf7.poster.avif?t=1740682738\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013550/extras/5f7d25f92dacef12c641f010bcfcfaf7.webm?t=1740682738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013550/extras/5f7d25f92dacef12c641f010bcfcfaf7.mp4?t=1740682738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>♦随时保存</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打开随时保存选项，在您离开的地方重新开始决斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>♦数码画廊</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在数码画廊中探索欣赏每个收录游戏的商品外观与说明书。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013550/extras/cd8199d13c1a25ee07b91ef47322855c.poster.avif?t=1740682738\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013550/extras/cd8199d13c1a25ee07b91ef47322855c.webm?t=1740682738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013550/extras/cd8199d13c1a25ee07b91ef47322855c.mp4?t=1740682738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收录游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013550/extras/a57e7178257011b6c040bbca16aa278d.poster.avif?t=1740682738\" width=480 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013550/extras/a57e7178257011b6c040bbca16aa278d.webm?t=1740682738\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013550/extras/a57e7178257011b6c040bbca16aa278d.mp4?t=1740682738\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Monsters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Monsters II: Dark Duel Stories</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. Yu-Gi-Oh! Monster Capsule</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. Yu-Gi-Oh! Dark Duel Stories</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5. Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Monsters 4: Battle of Great Duelists</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6. Yu-Gi-Oh! Dungeon Dice Monsters</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7. Yu-Gi-Oh! The Eternal Duelist Soul</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8. Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Monsters 6: Expert 2*</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9. Yu-Gi-Oh! The Sacred Cards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10. Yu-Gi-Oh! Reshef of Destruction</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >11. Yu-Gi-Oh! Worldwide Edition: Stairway to the Destined Duel</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12. Yu-Gi-Oh! World Championship Tournament 2004</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >13. Yu-Gi-Oh! Destiny Board Traveler</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >14. Yu-Gi-Oh! 7 Trials to Glory: World Championship Tournament 2005 (Yu-Gi-Oh! Day of the Duelist: World Championship Tournament 2005)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*「Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Monsters 6: Expert 2 」将以日语发行。您可以通过「 Yu-Gi-Oh! Worldwide Edition: Stairway」 中搭载的其他语言体验「Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Monsters 6: Expert 2」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >遊☆戯☆王 简介</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「遊☆戯☆王」是高桥和希老师原作，从1996年起在株式会社集英社的「週刊少年JUMP」连载，大受欢迎的漫画作品。电视动画从系列早期的「遊☆戯☆王デュエルモンスターズ」(Duel Monsters)开始在东京电视台系统播出，2022年4月起开始播映最新系列的「遊☆戯☆王ゴーラッシュ！！」(Go Rush!)，不断将「遊☆戯☆王」系列作品推向高峰。KONAMI DIGITAL ENTERTAINMENT从1998年起推出家用游戏，1999年起推出集换式卡牌游戏，为全世界的众多粉丝们带来无穷欢乐。</p>",
